program2: if else - odd even
--------
Pending 
TASK1: add condition to print that a is neither odd and neither even
test case: a=2, a=1, a=0.

class HelloWorld {
    
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Integer a = 3;

        if(a % 2 == 0){
            System.out.println("given number is even");
        }
        else {
            System.out.println("given number is odd");
        }
    }
    
}
